<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="night-n">night <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /naɪt/    美 /naɪt/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U] </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>夜；夜晚：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>in / during the night</strong> 
在夜里</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>far / late / deep into the night 
直到深夜</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I advise that you watch less TV <strong>at night</strong>.  
我建议你晚上少看点儿电视。</p><footer>译林④ – 2</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="all-night-long">all night (long)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>整夜：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I lay awake all night (long).
我整夜没睡着。</p></div>

<h3 id="night-and-day-day-and-night">night and day / day and night</h3>
<p>1.<strong>日日夜夜；夜以继日：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was so diligent that he worked day and night.
他非常勤奋，夜以继日地工作。</p><footer>2008 湖南书面表达</footer></div></div>